name: Lil Ethereum Vert
description: Lil Uzi Vert removed his $24 million pink forehead diamond implant. Sooo I replaced the diamond with an Ethereum ETH so that the image of the iconic forehead diamond will live on forever on the blockchain! This piece was inspired by a tweet from Lil Uzi Vert's Twitter in which he says at 1:31PM on Jan 30, 2021: "ethereum really works trust me." It's no secret Lil Uzi Vert is a supporter of cryptocurrency and this piece is a tribute to his support.
